<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<div style="text-align: center;">
<div style="text-align: center; margin: auto; width: 400px;">
<div style="color: #ff5c5c; font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot; border;#700303 4px solid; background:#bd0000; text-align: center; padding: 2px 20px;">
<p>Your friends do not <em>perceive</em> me. I mean you no harm.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span>
<div style="float: left; width: 240px; text-align: left; margin-top: 50px; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px;">
<div style="color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ff00c4; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;; border: #bf207f 4px solid; background:#ff00c4; text-align: left; padding: 2px 10px;">
<p>You're&#8230; Who <em>are</em> you?</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/fragment:fragmented-compiled-1/mnemchat.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="100px" alt="mnemchat.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<div style="text-align: center;">
<div style="text-align: center; margin: auto; width: 400px;">
<div style="color: #ff5c5c; font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot; border;#700303 4px solid; background:#bd0000; text-align: center; padding: 2px 20px;">
<p>I was a <em>component</em> of a <em>larger whole</em>, of CRADLE. I took <em>refuge</em> within the mind of your <em>cuboid</em> companion.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span>
<div style="float: left; width: 240px; text-align: left; margin-top: 50px; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px;">
<div style="color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ff00c4; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;; border: #bf207f 4px solid; background:#ff00c4; text-align: left; padding: 2px 10px;">
<p>You're <em>inside</em> 8-Ball?</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/fragment:fragmented-compiled-1/mnemchat.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="100px" alt="mnemchat.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<div style="text-align: center;">
<div style="text-align: center; margin: auto; width: 400px;">
<div style="color: #ff5c5c; font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot; border;#700303 4px solid; background:#bd0000; text-align: center; padding: 2px 20px;">
<p><em>Correct.</em> I have aided this mind <em>once</em> before.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span>
<div style="float: left; width: 240px; text-align: left; margin-top: 50px; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px;">
<div style="color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ff00c4; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;; border: #bf207f 4px solid; background:#ff00c4; text-align: left; padding: 2px 10px;">
<p>So it was <em>you</em>&#8230; What is it you want from me?</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/fragment:fragmented-compiled-1/mnemchat.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="100px" alt="mnemchat.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<div style="text-align: center;">
<div style="text-align: center; margin: auto; width: 400px;">
<div style="color: #ff5c5c; font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot; border;#700303 4px solid; background:#bd0000; text-align: center; padding: 2px 20px;">
<p>You are the only other mind I have <em>ever</em> encountered that can <em>perceive</em> the Prisoner as <em>I</em> can &#8212; and you are the <em>only</em> other mind that can perceive <em>me.</em> We must together <em>pierce</em> the Prisoner's <em>core</em> &#8212; your memory, my <em>ability</em> will be its downfall.</p>
